<%- include('partials/header') %>  

<div id="landing" class="pages">
  <div id="landingContent">
    <h1>Danene Copping</h1>
    <a href="#gallery">Browse my Gallery</a>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="gallery" class="pages">
  <h1>Gallery</h1>
  <% if(currentUser){ %>
    <a class="btn btn-success" href="/new">Add New Gallery</a>
  <% } %>
  <div>
    <% if(galleries.length != 0){ %>
      <div id="galleryCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img class="d-block" src="<%= galleries[0].image %>" alt="First slide">
          </div>
          <% for(let i = 1; i < galleries.length; i++){ %>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <img class="d-block" src="<%= galleries[i].image %>" alt="First slide">
            </div>
          <% } %>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#galleryCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#galleryCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
        <a class="btn btn-info" href="">View All</a>
      </div>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="about" class="pages">
  <div id="aboutContent" class="rounded">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <p>Danene Copping is a Canadian artist, experienced in various mediums, she excels in graphite/charcoal drawings.  It was very early in life that her parents saw an obvious gift and helped guide her talent, engaging her passion and from this all things creative grew.  Danene has spent her entire life drawing beautiful things, her attention to detail is what draws emotion from each piece and you cannot help but notice the pride she takes in the quality of her work. Danene continues to produce original pieces that portray the inherent beauty of nature as well as creating beautiful representations of loved family members.</p>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="contact" class="pages">
  <div id="contactContent" class="rounded">
    <h1>Contact</h1>
    <div class="headingDiv">
      <form action="/send" method="POST" enctype=”multipart/form-data”>
        <div class="form-group">
          <input class="form-control" type="text" name="fullName" placeholder="Full Name" required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <input class="form-control" type="email" name="email" placeholder="E-mail" required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <textarea class="form-control" type="text" name="message" placeholder="Message" required maxlength="6000" rows="6"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button class="btn btn-success">Send</button>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div id="socialMedia">
      <a class="mr-2" href="https://www.instagram.com/dcstudioartist/" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-facebook-square"></i></a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/dcstudioartist/" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-instagram-square"></i></a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <footer>
    <span><i class="far fa-copyright"></i> Danene Copping 2020 - All rights reserved</span>
  </footer>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
